        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mt-3">투자 서비스</h2>
        <p class="text-white/40 mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">고객의 투자 목표와 위험 성향에 맞춘 맞춤형 솔루션</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="reveal bg-[#0F1A2E] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-[#00D4AA]/20 transition-all duration-500 group" style="--delay: 1;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#00D4AA]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-[#00D4AA]/20 transition">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#00D4AA]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-white text-lg mb-2">자산 운용</h3>
